    org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EStructuralFeature.Internal.DynamicValueHolder, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject, ActuatorSystem, CyberPhysicalSystem, EngineSystem, RoboticSystem, System

    public class EngineSystemImpl
extends ActuatorSystemImpl
implements EngineSystem
    An implementation of the model object 'Engine System'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Vehicle Traction
    • Max Engine Force
    • Max Breaking Force
    • Max Allowed Steering
    • Max Allowed Velocity
    • Gear ration
